## üìö Educational Use Notice

This curriculum is specifically designed for educational purposes and is free to use for:
- Personal learning and skill development
- Educational institutions and training programs
- Mentoring and coaching activities
- Community workshops and bootcamps
- Open source contributions and improvements

## ü§ù Community Commitment

By using this curriculum, you agree to:
- Maintain the open source and educational nature of the content
- Give proper attribution when using substantial portions
- Share improvements back with the community when possible
- Help create an inclusive learning environment for all

## üåü Attribution

If you use this curriculum in your projects, courses, or tutorials, please include:
- Link back to the original repository
- Credit to "Web Development Learning Path by Mohit Suthar & Contributors"
- Mention that it's an open source educational project

**Example attribution:**
"Based on the Web Development Learning Path by Mohit Suthar & Contributors 
(https://github.com/MohitSutharOfficial/Webdev-fundamentals) - 
An open source curriculum for learning web development from beginner to senior level."
